des:
IntriCloud is the ProAV solution allows you to control HDMI network extenders, A/V matrixes, digital power supplies and other connected devices.

To use IntriCloud services, you must have a valid Intrising IntriClouds account. 
You can use this skill after login and can do nothing without login.
